+ *     All src and dst folios remain locked throughout Phase 1.
+ *
+ *   Phase 2 — Single batch flush (ONE IPI for all N pages):
+ *     try_to_unmap_flush() → arch_tlbbatch_flush() → one flush_tlb_mm_range
